<font color="#FF0000">NURSES IN VIETNAM</font><br>
<tt>Sun Apr 27  2:30:57 US/Eastern 1997
</tt><p>
I did not go to VietNam but many of the nurses I went to diploma RN school with in Cincinnati did go in order to get their education paid for. I've spent the past 25 years as an emergency nurse now - I look around at my big city ED and am so thankful for what the nurses, medics and docs learned in VietNam that have changed what we do in emergency care. To my colleagues...you will never be forgotten<br><br>
